<!DOCTYPE html>
 
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <title></title>
        <style>
            h1{text-decoration: :overline}
            h2{text-decoration: :underline}
            h3{text-decoration: :line-through}
            a{text-decoration: :none}
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>這是標題</h1>
        <h2>這是標題</h2>
        <h3>這是標題</h3>
        <a href="."這是連結</a> /   a{text-decoration: :none} (把連結取消底線)
    </body>
    text-decoration可用來裝飾文字
    overline-在文字上方增加線條
    underline-文字增加底線
    line-through在文字中增加刪除線
    none-預設值，沒加任何的特效
</html>
